No. 181,

Misc.

Rupp v. Teets, Warden. A. J. Zirpoli for petitioner. Edmund G. Brown, Attorney General of California, Clarence A. Linn, Assistant Attorney General, and Arlo E. Smith, Deputy Attorney General, for respondent.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of California granted.
